{"tid":2162953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留守議會嘅泛民，你們冇資格同香港人，繼續風雨同路去守護香港","createTime":"2020-08-18T11:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T11:41:30.000Z","uid":52764,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee20d9b86ff8c539aef95678342a56d31b59b5d","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"究竟泛民係咪唔明白「臨立會」，<br />\n係共產黨專登設局去陰你地，<br />\n令支持者放棄你地，<br />\n變相中共可以加快步伐殘害香港人。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地都係堅持留守議會，<br />\n好坦白講你無資格同香港人並肩作戰，<br />\n你地以為可以用一年時間可以抵抗惡法通過，如果真係如你所願，<br />\n咁呢幾年嚟話比香港人聽，你地完全係失職，<br />\n並無出盡全力去幫香港人守住議會，<br />\n而家先嚟話守住條防線，<br />\n不如你地直接承認係貪錢咁咪仲好。"},{"pid":"01d77fb718761aa5dcc83a72f272fae3dede4aed","tid":2162953,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"根本應該去英國成立流亡議會"},{"pid":"95589c4c02102c9ba93b01255f6efe42585e5bd5","tid":2162953,"uid":257184,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"收爹啦死分化撚<br />\n分化撚死全家"},{"pid":"8b61be84c946d357ee0e9d0aca7797e81fd9364e","tid":2162953,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"以二級議會, 解決去留爭議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2162332/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2162332/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3f3a07ea541a7ff936f0de231860f1b0dbeb265a","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"187e8cd7f4081081d9a64314d0221d7a12642402","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"613a5ac7d66d4a18a238020c2c068564c479f4be","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"375f09e90f6e20f06744314b28c51a19b5ddaccf","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:34:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c29e17a420edd0be4d0f65c7a317993c3f08ee3","tid":2162953,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"我相信到時會有人走，有人留，但留嘅請你哋出返份聲明<br />\n<br />\n1. 你哋再唔係代議仕<br />\n<br />\n2. 四年任期已過，你哋係被委任嘅前議會<br />\n<br />\n3. 你哋之後係議會投嘅所有票，做嘅所有行動，同四年前投你票嘅選民無關，所有決定及行動後果由自己負責 （其實留得嘅九成係大黨，係咪真係同選民無關有腦嘅都識諗）<br />\n<br />\n（大家諗到乜嘢可以加上去）<br />\n____________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n當然，市民到時亦無權要求你捐任何薪酬出黎去支持任何組織（你捐係你自願，市民之後無權迫你做任何野，但你唔捐到時投票就你個黨數）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個....好可能係團結返大部份人嘅方法...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人認為留係可以嘅，下年唔玩嘅咪留低入去搞囉，始終點都要有人企咪兜發言"},{"pid":"f07c0c7489ae57e72e3988bb3c615b42f03ce852","tid":2162953,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔尊重民意，一意孤行先係問題"},{"pid":"1e5bd3f83491985152a82b94f0762b5254ca0401","tid":2162953,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07c0c7489ae57e72e3988bb3c615b42f03ce852","tid":2162953,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔尊重民意，一意孤行先係問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"仲要唔積極提出選舉要如期舉行<br />\n明明呢個係得到國際支持"},{"pid":"6bc6d993e349c38f97bea64280e6ad972461a1ff","tid":2162953,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"因非法拖延選舉而產生嘅所謂臨立會本身就冇晒合法性，仲衷個頭埋去承認佢。 睇唔透。"},{"pid":"06df6bee6116763e4faea58965bf8ce363acea27","tid":2162953,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a0d4fab97974fa5af2032531303ddd2876a81d1","tid":2162953,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14ec664998e34f0dbb1366364780adc67a47513e","tid":216295